1
00:00:00,298 --> 00:00:02,637
-LY FIFTH, NINETEEN NINETY SIX.

2
00:00:02,982 --> 00:00:08,038
MISTER BAKER, ir zen- ir hot ah gehert tsu di ah, tsum di bund?

3
00:00:07,572 --> 00:00:08,511
yo.

4
00:00:09,580 --> 00:00:12,037
ven zent ir gevorn dortn a mitglid?

5
00:00:12,178 --> 00:00:14,231
ikh bin gevorn a mitglid

6
00:00:14,490 --> 00:00:17,094
ven ikh bin alt geven zibetsn yor

7
00:00:17,094 --> 00:00:19,597
als a yidisher arbets mentsh

8
00:00:19,873 --> 00:00:23,242
un ikh hob shoyn a bisl gelezn un farshtanen

9
00:00:23,316 --> 00:00:27,090
az me darf zikh farbindn mit a gevise organizatsye

10
00:00:27,349 --> 00:00:31,106
un der bundisher yugnt iz geven a bavustziniker yugnt

11
00:00:31,348 --> 00:00:32,962
un mir hobn gegat

12
00:00:33,137 --> 00:00:34,987
a- undzer, der LEADER

13
00:00:35,533 --> 00:00:42,665
iz gevezn a mentsh a, a gebildeter mentsh, hot geendikt tsvey fakultetn. zayn nomen iz gevezn

14
00:00:42,992 --> 00:00:44,558
UNK KLEPFISZ

15
00:00:44,558 --> 00:00:48,386
hagam dem KLEPFISZ'S a kuzin, ir veyst fun dem KLEPFISZ vos er

16
00:00:48,747 --> 00:00:50,549
⟨iz yetst⟩ a, a shrayber.

17
00:00:49,303 --> 00:00:50,481
in Yisroel.

18
00:00:50,549 --> 00:00:51,254
ye.

19
00:00:51,936 --> 00:00:56,975
un dortn, ikh hob, in di organizatsye bin ikh geven aktiv

20
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,676
un mir hobn gegat a khor

21
00:00:59,749 --> 00:01:02,696
in di organizatsye fun finef un zibetsik

22
00:01:03,276 --> 00:01:05,902
yugntlekhe, yinglekh un meydlekh.

23
00:01:06,043 --> 00:01:08,467
mir hobn gehat a dramatishn krayz

24
00:01:08,625 --> 00:01:12,821
ikh hob gezungen in khor. ikh hob geshpilt in dramatishn krayz oykh.

25
00:01:13,485 --> 00:01:19,790
UND, azoy iz ongeganen. mir hobn gegat lektsyes. mir flegn aropbrengen

26
00:01:19,898 --> 00:01:21,461
fun Varshe

27
00:01:21,653 --> 00:01:23,216
di shraybers

28
00:01:23,695 --> 00:01:26,898
vos ⟨m'hot gemakht⟩ forlezung kimat yedn shabes

29
00:01:26,898 --> 00:01:29,493
flegt undz aropkumen fun Varshe

30
00:01:29,635 --> 00:01:34,624
⟨di⟩ shraybers vos hobn geshribn in, in di folks tsaytung oder andere shraybers.

31
00:01:34,849 --> 00:01:40,631
un yedn shabes UNK iz gevezn azan hoyz. s'hot geheysn oyf poylish DOM LUDOWY.

32
00:01:40,654 --> 00:01:42,302
s'heyst a folks hoyz

33
00:01:42,325 --> 00:01:45,306
un dortn flegn forkumen di lektsyes.

34
00:01:45,750 --> 00:01:47,178
un

35
00:01:47,488 --> 00:01:51,819
un ikh hob gelernt dortn zeyer a sakh in di organizatsye.

36
00:01:52,872 --> 00:01:57,996
andere geshvister h- h- zenen oykh geven mitglider in, in bund?

37
00:01:57,715 --> 00:01:59,801
mayn bru- mayns a bruder.

38
00:01:59,908 --> 00:02:02,804
mayn elterer bruder iz geven a POYLE tsienist.

39
00:02:05,106 --> 00:02:10,010
un vos mit di andere kinder? zenen zey geven religyez tsi nit azoy?

40
00:02:08,699 --> 00:02:12,629
NO, bay un- di kinder ⟨zey⟩ zenen nisht geven religyez.

41
00:02:12,629 --> 00:02:16,089
mayn foter iz gevezn a yid vos er iz geganen davenen

42
00:02:14,218 --> 00:02:15,595
der eyntsiker

43
00:02:16,089 --> 00:02:17,590
ober di kinder

44
00:02:17,590 --> 00:02:19,697
zenen nisht gevezn

45
00:02:20,698 --> 00:02:24,590
v- ven m'iz geven yung, hot men nokh gemuzt leygn tfiln

46
00:02:24,664 --> 00:02:27,560
un geyn davenen, nor ven m'iz gevorn elter

47
00:02:27,668 --> 00:02:30,024
ven di eltern hobn shoyn nisht gegat

48
00:02:30,435 --> 00:02:32,116
keyn hashpoe gor

49
00:02:30,638 --> 00:02:32,117
UNK

50
00:02:32,258 --> 00:02:37,871
iz hobn di kinder zikh oysgelebt vi fraye mentshn, ober m'iz geven, geven yidn. m'hot ge-

51
00:02:38,946 --> 00:02:40,335
veltlekhe yidn.

52
00:02:40,324 --> 00:02:42,630
hobn di eltern gezogt epes vegn dem?

53
00:02:42,298 --> 00:02:46,662
di eltern zenen geven a bisl nisht tsufridn far vos mir geyen nisht in shul arayn.

54
00:02:47,142 --> 00:02:49,076
tsum bayshpil, yomkiper

55
00:02:49,572 --> 00:02:52,148
hot men bay undz in shtub nisht gekent esn.

56
00:02:53,031 --> 00:03:00,292
iz UNK ⟨vi als⟩ veltlekhe mentshn vos hobn yo gevolt esn, hobn zey geganen in di organizatsye. dortn geven

57
00:03:00,292 --> 00:03:02,469
UNK ver s'hot gevolt hot gegesn

58
00:03:02,469 --> 00:03:03,909
ober nisht in shtub.

59
00:03:05,046 --> 00:03:07,807
vos iz geven di bafelkerung fun Gritse?

60
00:03:08,151 --> 00:03:11,471
s'iz geven bay z- bay di zeks toyznt yidn.

61
00:03:11,471 --> 00:03:15,001
s'iz zekhtsik protsent fun di bafelkerung zenen geven yidn

62
00:03:17,297 --> 00:03:18,489
un

63
00:03:17,533 --> 00:03:20,716
az umgefar finef, ah fir toyznt goyim.

64
00:03:20,824 --> 00:03:25,813
n- yo, s'iz geven nor, ven zenen forgekumen, gedorfn forkumen

65
00:03:26,055 --> 00:03:28,327
valn. dos heyst ELECTION

66
00:03:28,485 --> 00:03:30,532
tsu di CITY HALL UNK

67
00:03:30,532 --> 00:03:34,250
voltn, ven yidn UNK voltn zey dokh gekent ibernemen

68
00:03:34,425 --> 00:03:35,966
hobn di polyakn

69
00:03:35,966 --> 00:03:38,638
tsuge⟨CONNECTED⟩ derfer

70
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:40,561
tsu di shtot

71
00:03:40,821 --> 00:03:44,662
azoy arum, s'iz geven derfer nisht vayt fun shtot.

72
00:03:45,158 --> 00:03:49,303
iz hot men ⟨vos⟩ fir, finef kilometer fun di shtot iz geven derfer

73
00:03:49,393 --> 00:03:54,112
hobn zey tsu⟨CONNECTED⟩ az zey gehern tsu di shtot. azoy arum hobn zey gegat a merheyt.

74
00:03:54,945 --> 00:03:58,179
flegt ir a mol aroysforn fun Gritse als yingl?

75
00:03:57,426 --> 00:03:59,833
o, ikh fleg zeyer oft forn keyn Varshe.

76
00:04:00,025 --> 00:04:01,301
vos iz geven

77
00:04:00,177 --> 00:04:02,955
vayl fun undz tsu forn keyn Varshe hot genumen

78
00:04:03,265 --> 00:04:04,659
dray fertl sho.

79
00:04:04,530 --> 00:04:05,958
vos iz geven in Varshe?

80
00:04:05,998 --> 00:04:07,747
di hoypt shtot fun Poyln.

81
00:04:07,838 --> 00:04:10,211
ober tsulib vos zent ir dortn geforn?

82
00:04:09,778 --> 00:04:13,484
bin geforn vayl m'hot opgegesn shabes dos tsholnt

83
00:04:13,778 --> 00:04:19,779
hot men zikh oyfgezetst ⟨oyf d-⟩ a BUS vos iz gegangen keyn Varshe. s'iz geven a komunikatsye vos hot geheysn

84
00:04:19,937 --> 00:04:21,247
P.K.P.

85
00:04:21,490 --> 00:04:26,867
dos iz geganen a- RADOM, WARSZAWA, fun Rodem keyn Varshe, iz oykh gegangen durkh GROJEC.

86
00:04:27,058 --> 00:04:31,355
hot genumen dray fertl sho. bin arayngeforn. m'iz geganen in a tea-

87
00:04:30,214 --> 00:04:31,372
oyf shabes?

88
00:04:31,497 --> 00:04:32,807
shabes, yo.

89
00:04:33,117 --> 00:04:35,493
m'iz geforn shabes ⟨vayl⟩ m'iz nisht geven keyn

90
00:04:35,493 --> 00:04:37,970
iz men geven in a, in a teater

91
00:04:38,331 --> 00:04:40,789
un far, bay di nakht zenen mir aheymgekumen.

92
00:04:44,203 --> 00:04:47,352
ven hot dos alts ongehoybn tsu endern?

93
00:04:48,270 --> 00:04:49,850
mitn oysbrokh

94
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:51,858
fun di milkhome.

95
00:04:52,658 --> 00:04:53,811
nisht frier?

96
00:04:53,811 --> 00:04:55,456
in, in zibn un akhtsik?

97
00:04:55,408 --> 00:04:56,262
vegn

98
00:04:55,456 --> 00:04:58,609
in zibn un, un draysik oder in zeks un draysik

99
00:04:56,809 --> 00:04:57,765
vegn v-

100
00:04:57,990 --> 00:05:00,043
vegn vos s'iz forgekumen?

101
00:04:58,969 --> 00:05:00,600
s'iz, ⟨zenen men⟩ geven

102
00:05:00,994 --> 00:05:04,380
gezetstn antkegn di yidn, spetsifishe gezetsn?

103
00:05:04,183 --> 00:05:09,442
yo. s'iz gevezn az der premye minister hot gezogt az me meg boykotirn yidn.

104
00:05:09,398 --> 00:05:10,826
ober akhuts dem.

105
00:05:10,782 --> 00:05:14,691
iz forge- ongefaln az a polyak hot zikh ongeshikert

106
00:05:14,848 --> 00:05:19,786
hot zikh gevolt makhn freylekh, iz er aroysgan, hot er gezen a yid mit a bord, hoybt er on tsu shlogn

107
00:05:20,485 --> 00:05:25,001
un oyb yidn hobn geshtelt a vidershtand, zenen bald geven politsey.

108
00:05:25,193 --> 00:05:26,177
nor

109
00:05:26,177 --> 00:05:30,435
ven di goyim hobn geshlogn yidn, hot men politsey ge- nisht keyn politsey gezen.

110
00:05:36,263 --> 00:05:41,539
az vos iz geshen in nayn un, un draysik? ir gedenkt ven di milkhome hot zikh oysgebrokhn?

111
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:45,454
ye. bin geven in, ⟨ge- ven⟩ di milkhome iz oysgebrokhn

112
00:05:46,371 --> 00:05:51,275
hot genumen n- n- m'hot zikh keyner nisht forgeshtelt

113
00:05:51,568 --> 00:05:56,742
az dos vet azoy shnel, az der daytsh vet azoy shnel bazign Poyln.

114
00:05:57,019 --> 00:05:59,409
in meshekh fun di tsveyte vokh

115
00:05:59,432 --> 00:06:01,771
iz der daytsh geven bay undz in shtot.

116
00:06:02,942 --> 00:06:04,134
ven iz dos geven?

117
00:06:04,393 --> 00:06:09,449
dos iz geven, di milkhome iz oysgebrokhn, oyb ikh makh nisht keyn toes, in september.

118
00:06:10,283 --> 00:06:11,441
iz azoy

119
00:06:12,358 --> 00:06:17,448
dem fuftsntn oder dem akhtsntn, ikh ken nisht ⟨s'iz⟩ shoyn fuftsik yor gedenken

120
00:06:17,488 --> 00:06:20,958
zenen di daytshn geven bay undz in shtot, ober nisht Varshe.

121
00:06:20,958 --> 00:06:23,198
dos iz geven unter Va- bay undz in shtot.

122
00:06:23,074 --> 00:06:24,165
in Gritse?

123
00:06:23,766 --> 00:06:24,890
in Gritse.

124
00:06:24,913 --> 00:06:26,594
ven zey zenen arayn

125
00:06:27,377 --> 00:06:30,493
iz bald oyfn tsveytn tog

126
00:06:31,225 --> 00:06:33,643
zenen, ⟨gebn⟩ a kum on a bande

127
00:06:33,643 --> 00:06:36,213
mit di S.S., di GESTAPO.

128
00:06:37,266 --> 00:06:39,844
un di yidishe bafelkerung

129
00:06:39,844 --> 00:06:41,664
iz gevorn hefker

130
00:06:42,683 --> 00:06:45,849
azoy vi a bande tseyushete bestyes.

131
00:06:46,210 --> 00:06:50,524
s'iz beemes nisht geven tsu farshteyn vi azoy eyn mentsh

132
00:06:50,614 --> 00:06:55,285
ken dos tun tsu a tsveytn mentsh. m'hot gere- geharget, gerabirt

133
00:06:55,285 --> 00:06:56,463
g- fargvaldikt

134
00:06:56,487 --> 00:06:59,096
dos iz gevorn, der yid iz gevorn hefker.

135
00:06:59,693 --> 00:07:02,134
m'iz farforn m- mit TRUCKS

136
00:07:02,241 --> 00:07:08,259
un m'hot aroysgenumen UNK s'iz geven manufaktur skhoyre, hobn zey aroysgenumen di skhoyre, di besere skhoyres.

137
00:07:08,282 --> 00:07:12,781
s'iz geven leder gevelber, ⟨hobn⟩ zey tsugeforn mit TRUCKS. m'hot aroysgenumen di leder

138
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:17,796
un di gemeyne, di ⟨azolkh⟩ gemeyne shtiklekh hot men gevorfn aroys in gas

139
00:07:17,796 --> 00:07:19,835
un UNK mit polyakn

140
00:07:20,078 --> 00:07:22,485
zenen gelofn un hobn gekhapt dos.

141
00:07:22,980 --> 00:07:25,812
un, un s'iz gevezn der yid

142
00:07:25,812 --> 00:07:28,914
m'hot yedn tog iz gekumen an andere gezeyre

143
00:07:29,072 --> 00:07:31,333
do me zol tsushteln yidn

144
00:07:31,333 --> 00:07:35,813
ts- oyf, tsu d- oyf, ⟨az⟩ me zol arbetn, hot men zey aroysgefirt in mark

145
00:07:36,109 --> 00:07:39,444
un m'hot geshlogn un gepaynikt az zey hobn gemuzt

146
00:07:39,518 --> 00:07:41,317
tantsn oyf ale fir

147
00:07:41,442 --> 00:07:44,372
un polyakn di na- azelkhe

148
00:07:44,378 --> 00:07:50,497
nisht blo- bavustzinik, zenen geshtanen un hobn gelakht un gefreyt zikh, nisht kukndik vos zey aleyn zenen gevezn

149
00:07:50,773 --> 00:07:53,214
okupirt dortn fun dem soyne

150
00:07:54,317 --> 00:07:55,188
UND

151
00:07:55,448 --> 00:07:57,669
di geshikhte d- tsv- tf-

152
00:07:57,878 --> 00:08:00,521
ir hot dos alts gezen mit di eygene oygn?

153
00:07:59,329 --> 00:08:03,727
⟨vos⟩ ikh bin geven in Gritse, vu ikh hob gegat di meglekhkeyt tsu zen

154
00:08:03,733 --> 00:08:06,461
⟨vi⟩ m'hot gekhapt yidn tsu di arbet

155
00:08:06,619 --> 00:08:07,966
iz bekers

156
00:08:07,966 --> 00:08:11,119
hot men nisht ge- hot men nisht gekhapt tsu keyn arbet

157
00:08:11,479 --> 00:08:15,573
iz vi azoy vi ikh bin geven a kamashn makher, hob ikh zikh ongetun in a vays fartekh

158
00:08:15,573 --> 00:08:18,453
un ikh hob oyfgegebn. ikh bin ⟨arop⟩ in undzer bekeray

159
00:08:19,022 --> 00:08:23,319
iz zenen arayn, hobn zey in a por tog shpeter gemakht a gezeyre

160
00:08:23,460 --> 00:08:25,954
azoy vi s'iz do tsvelef bekerayen

161
00:08:25,954 --> 00:08:28,415
yidishe un dray poylishe

162
00:08:28,590 --> 00:08:30,423
hot men nayn farmakht

163
00:08:30,784 --> 00:08:33,254
dray yidishe hot men gelozt bakn

164
00:08:33,254 --> 00:08:36,314
un dray poylishe. keyn yid hot nisht getort koyfn

165
00:08:36,314 --> 00:08:37,682
bay di poylishe

166
00:08:37,682 --> 00:08:40,565
un di poylishe hobn nisht getort koyfn bay keyn yidn.

167
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:43,079
undzer bekeray iz geven farmakht.

168
00:08:44,082 --> 00:08:45,814
in a gevisn tog

169
00:08:46,377 --> 00:08:49,746
iz geven nokh mitog sh- bin ikh geshtanen far dem gevelb

170
00:08:49,887 --> 00:08:52,328
iz farforn a daytsher ofitsir

171
00:08:52,485 --> 00:08:53,846
mit a TRUCKl

172
00:08:54,207 --> 00:08:59,955
un er iz aroysgeganen un zogt tsu mir "zenen SIE der baker mayster?" zog ikh im "JA."

173
00:09:00,349 --> 00:09:03,600
zogt er er darft hobn tsvey hundert un fuftsik

174
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:06,840
shtiklekh epl kukhn, tsi ikh ken dos im makhn.

175
00:09:07,318 --> 00:09:12,560
zog ikh im "JA, ikh ken dos makhn DEN SIE HABEN di produkt-" ir f- ir farshteyt vos ikh zog.

176
00:09:13,275 --> 00:09:14,875
zogt er "JA, ikh hob"

177
00:09:14,875 --> 00:09:19,259
in Gritse iz gevezn tsvey parove miln, groyse miln

178
00:09:19,266 --> 00:09:21,617
un s'iz geven ongeladevet mit mel

179
00:09:21,617 --> 00:09:24,468
un dos iz shoyn gevezn alts der daytsh hot gekent

180
00:09:24,468 --> 00:09:25,959
tun vos er hot gevolt

181
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,761
hot er gebrengt a zak mit mel

182
00:09:28,986 --> 00:09:31,376
hot gebrengt tsvey kestlekh epl

183
00:09:31,433 --> 00:09:34,312
hot gebrengt, alts tsugenumen bay yidn, farshtendlekh.

184
00:09:34,639 --> 00:09:37,437
m'hot gebrengt ts- tsuker un farshidene

185
00:09:37,437 --> 00:09:40,067
m'hot gekent opbakn di toyznt shtiklekh

186
00:09:40,275 --> 00:09:42,659
un ikh hob im dos

187
00:09:42,659 --> 00:09:45,179
dem bekeray, bay undz hot men dos opgebakn.

188
00:09:45,608 --> 00:09:50,490
tsu morgns iz er gekumen. m'hot im gegebn -gebn a kave tsu farzukhn.

189
00:09:50,490 --> 00:09:51,879
s'iz WUNDERBAR

190
00:09:52,155 --> 00:09:53,845
un fun dem tog on

191
00:09:53,845 --> 00:09:57,845
hot undzer BAKERY ongehoybn tsu bakn bloyz far daytshn.

192
00:09:57,994 --> 00:10:00,379
a daytsh iz arayngekumen, hot genumen

193
00:10:00,379 --> 00:10:03,298
a kilo zeml, hot er ibergelozt a tsetl

194
00:10:03,298 --> 00:10:07,694
tsvey kiles vifl. mit di tsetelekh ze'mir geganen in di komendatur

195
00:10:07,694 --> 00:10:11,921
un dortn hobn mir geku- mir bakumen mel fun di, fun di mil

196
00:10:11,921 --> 00:10:16,517
azoy ven ikh bin geforn in di mil mit a daytshn oyfn motor⟨CYC⟩

197
00:10:17,282 --> 00:10:19,874
hob ikh gezen in mark vos m'hot getun

198
00:10:19,932 --> 00:10:22,761
vi me harget di yidn, vi me paynikt zey.

199
00:10:23,728 --> 00:10:25,728
der daytsh vos er iz mit mir geforn

200
00:10:25,728 --> 00:10:28,028
hot er tsu mir gegebn a kuk, zogt er

201
00:10:28,028 --> 00:10:30,169
"DIE JUDEN HABEN KRIEG GEWOLLT"

202
00:10:30,681 --> 00:10:33,138
az di yidn hobn krig gevolt, derfar hot

203
00:10:33,668 --> 00:10:35,130
tuen zey dos

204
00:10:35,743 --> 00:10:37,672
UND der daytsh

205
00:10:37,672 --> 00:10:40,305
iz gevezn nisht kaza bestye.

206
00:10:40,305 --> 00:10:42,319
er iz geven a daytsh a mentsh

207
00:10:43,253 --> 00:10:49,793
in a por tog, ven er hot zikh, hot moyre gehat tsu ⟨redn⟩, ven ikh hob zikh mit im bafrayndet, er fleg yedn tog kumen nemen

208
00:10:49,793 --> 00:10:51,343
ge- gebeks

209
00:10:51,657 --> 00:10:53,760
hot er ge- nakher gebrengt

210
00:10:54,188 --> 00:10:57,433
akht breytlekh, zeks broyt militerishe

211
00:10:57,433 --> 00:10:59,396
un er hot gezogt tsu mayn muter

212
00:10:59,588 --> 00:11:03,075
"FRAU Beker, GEBEN SIE DASS far di oreme JUDEN."

213
00:11:03,672 --> 00:11:04,847
der daytsh

214
00:11:05,511 --> 00:11:08,492
un ikh hob zikh mit v- d- er iz gevezn

215
00:11:09,055 --> 00:11:13,588
bay undz in di shtot bay tsvey vokhn. yedn tog flegt er kumen.

216
00:11:13,695 --> 00:11:16,119
er iz geven a mobilizirte

217
00:11:16,243 --> 00:11:20,928
in di armey, un ikh hob oysgefunen ⟨nor bloyz⟩ er iz geven a lerer fun di heym.

218
00:11:21,525 --> 00:11:25,181
un ven er iz avek, iz er ongekumen, hot mir gezogt

219
00:11:25,288 --> 00:11:26,480
"her Beker

220
00:11:26,622 --> 00:11:29,147
FAHREN SIE AB nokh OST

221
00:11:29,254 --> 00:11:31,846
ES vet SCHLIMM SEIN MIT JUDEN"

222
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:34,074
bay di, in, in, bay dem daytsh.

223
00:11:35,447 --> 00:11:37,562
ven er hot mir dos gezogt

224
00:11:37,562 --> 00:11:39,188
hot zikh mit mir gezegnt

225
00:11:39,261 --> 00:11:41,162
iz dos mir arayn in kop

226
00:11:42,062 --> 00:11:46,781
az UNK s'iz nishto, me darf zen vos UNK zol antloyfn

227
00:11:47,935 --> 00:11:51,017
hob ikh nokh in a tsvey vokhn shpeter

228
00:11:51,057 --> 00:11:53,315
hob ikh zikh oyfgehoybn mit mayn

229
00:11:53,315 --> 00:11:54,561
tsvey brider

230
00:11:55,292 --> 00:12:01,546
un ikh hob mitgenumen mayn froy. mir zenen nisht geven nokh farheyrat, a meydl vos mir zenen gants tsuzamen in shule

231
00:12:02,785 --> 00:12:04,568
un mir zenen avek

232
00:12:04,995 --> 00:12:10,220
tsu di grenets bay Malkin. dos iz geven di grenets tsvishn Poyln

233
00:12:10,412 --> 00:12:14,236
un di sovyetn, vayl di, di sovyetn zenen gekumen

234
00:12:14,428 --> 00:12:16,059
fun di EAST SIDE

235
00:12:16,268 --> 00:12:20,177
un di daytshn zenen gekumen fun di WEST SIDE, un zey hobn gemakht

236
00:12:20,402 --> 00:12:23,332
di grenets bay BREST LITOVSK.

237
00:12:23,592 --> 00:12:29,171
mir zenen tsugeforn tsu a shtot vos hot geheysn Malkin vos iz bay di grenets

238
00:12:28,806 --> 00:12:30,049
ven iz dos geven?

239
00:12:30,510 --> 00:12:35,212
dos iz geven azoy in S- in oktober, ikh denk in ende oktober

240
00:12:35,455 --> 00:12:36,849
nayn un draysik.

241
00:12:36,568 --> 00:12:38,084
eyder me geyt vayter

242
00:12:38,084 --> 00:12:41,906
tsi gedenkt ir di nemen fun etlekhe onfirers

243
00:12:41,906 --> 00:12:43,568
der daytsh vos hot aykh

244
00:12:43,568 --> 00:12:45,050
bavornt aroys

245
00:12:44,027 --> 00:12:49,117
leyder gedenk ikh nisht, un ikh hob moyre gegat zikh tsu fregn oykhet, un er hot oykh moyre gegat.

246
00:12:48,921 --> 00:12:51,128
der S.S. onfirer vos es hot

247
00:12:51,128 --> 00:12:52,661
hot ersht ongehoybn

248
00:12:52,684 --> 00:12:54,630
mit, mit, mit di ale

249
00:12:54,630 --> 00:12:55,929
akhzoryes

250
00:12:55,929 --> 00:12:56,857
ah

251
00:12:56,751 --> 00:13:00,086
ikh bin nisht geven in kontakt mit keyn daytsh.

252
00:12:56,857 --> 00:12:58,415
ir gedenkt im?

253
00:13:00,143 --> 00:13:03,529
hot ir gekent etlekhe poylishe penemer?

254
00:13:03,889 --> 00:13:07,646
poylish hob ikh gekent a sakh, vos UNK bakent ale polyakn.

255
00:13:07,703 --> 00:13:11,713
ir zent geven frier fraynt oder koynim, oder

256
00:13:09,795 --> 00:13:16,859
zey hobn zikh b- YEAH, OH YEAH, zey hobn, bay mir, ale mayne CUSTOMERS vos zey hobn bay mir zikh geneyt zenen geven polyakn, shusters

257
00:13:16,444 --> 00:13:18,598
un zey zenen geshtanen un gelakht?

258
00:13:18,638 --> 00:13:24,977
di, a- di farshidene, zenen geshtanen ⟨vu⟩ m'hot yidn gepay- zenen geshtanen, hobn ge- khoyzek gemakht, yo.

259
00:13:23,802 --> 00:13:26,833
ir ge= ir gedenkt di nemen fun di mentshn?

260
00:13:27,008 --> 00:13:32,894
zikh gedenken, s- s'iz shver dortn tsu gedenken. ikh gedenk UNK ikh hob gehat eyn INCIDENT.

261
00:13:27,193 --> 00:13:28,300
fun di

262
00:13:32,894 --> 00:13:34,646
vos ikh vil do bamerkn

263
00:13:35,243 --> 00:13:38,763
ven ikh hob ge- shoyn ge- ven mir hobn shoyn gebakn

264
00:13:38,763 --> 00:13:41,643
nor mir hobn nisht getort farkoyfn far keyn tsivil

265
00:13:41,643 --> 00:13:45,727
ober far di mentshn vos zey hobn bar undz befor gekoyft hobn mir

266
00:13:45,727 --> 00:13:48,535
durkh an andere tir dos UNK yo gegebn.

267
00:13:48,675 --> 00:13:51,538
in a gevisn tog iz aropgekumen a polyak.

268
00:13:51,747 --> 00:13:53,935
er hot geheysn ⟨SLOWINSKI⟩

269
00:13:54,666 --> 00:13:58,220
zayn froy iz, er flegt bar undz koyfn. mir zenen geven noent

270
00:13:58,952 --> 00:14:03,384
un hot gezogt kh'zol im gebn tsvey broyt, tsvey ⟨azolkhe⟩ zeml

271
00:14:04,032 --> 00:14:07,755
un der daytsh, der ofitsir iz geshtanen in di BAKERY

272
00:14:08,672 --> 00:14:13,222
hob ikh im gezogt "ikh ken dir yetst nisht gebn. zest, ikh tor nisht farkoyfn keyn tsivile.

273
00:14:13,903 --> 00:14:18,909
hot er gezen, shteyt er, der ofitsir, hot er gegebn a makh tsun im oyf mir, "JUDE"

274
00:14:18,949 --> 00:14:20,563
az ikh bin a JUDE.

275
00:14:20,923 --> 00:14:23,679
un er hot nisht gevust az der ofitsir

276
00:14:23,679 --> 00:14:25,426
iz geven mayn ofitsir

277
00:14:25,426 --> 00:14:28,092
iz er arayngekumen, zogt er "WASS WOLL ER, DER SCHWEIN?"

278
00:14:28,092 --> 00:14:30,469
ir veyst, dos heyst, a SCHWEIN heyst a khazer.

279
00:14:30,643 --> 00:14:33,812
hob ikh gezogt "er vil dos BROT, ober ikh ken dokh nisht far-"

280
00:14:33,812 --> 00:14:35,964
hot er nokh gegebn azoy a

281
00:14:35,964 --> 00:14:38,653
a kop un aroysgesh- aroysgelofn.

282
00:14:38,997 --> 00:14:43,598
dos iz geven bald in onheyb, a mentsh vos hot mikh gut gekent, di gantse FAMILY

283
00:14:43,637 --> 00:14:45,436
hot er shoyn gezogt JUDE

284
00:14:47,130 --> 00:14:48,491
un voltn

285
00:14:48,784 --> 00:14:50,972
di, di antisemitn

286
00:14:51,990 --> 00:14:55,477
nisht nor vos zey hobn ⟨gevolt⟩ tsum bayshpil bahaltn ⟨vuhin⟩

287
00:14:55,686 --> 00:14:58,262
s'hot ge⟨UNK⟩ toyt shtrof far bahaltn a yid

288
00:14:58,538 --> 00:15:00,236
ober nisht onvayzn

289
00:15:00,867 --> 00:15:04,658
ven es zenen arayn di, vi azoy vi di vilde bestyes

290
00:15:04,832 --> 00:15:09,216
hobn, un polyakn hobn z- un s'iz geven tsevishn zey VOLKSDEUTSCHEN

291
00:15:09,216 --> 00:15:10,580
zey hobn geredt poylish

292
00:15:10,688 --> 00:15:15,137
hobn zey polyakn ongevor- ongevizn vu es iz, ver s'iz a raykher yid

293
00:15:15,278 --> 00:15:17,297
flegn zey geyn in di hayzer

294
00:15:17,539 --> 00:15:20,970
un makhn revizyes, un vos zey hobn gefunen a tsirung

295
00:15:20,970 --> 00:15:24,401
gold, vos, ⟨hobn zey⟩ alts tsugenumen un nokh tseshlogn di mentshn

296
00:15:25,487 --> 00:15:28,889
un ⟨v- eyder⟩ ikh bin nokh avekgeforn, ikh hob fargesn

297
00:15:29,031 --> 00:15:31,691
iz geven, Varshe iz nisht geven genumen

298
00:15:32,153 --> 00:15:33,783
iz gekumen a bafel

299
00:15:33,783 --> 00:15:38,383
ale mener fun fuftsn biz finef un fuftsik yor

300
00:15:38,383 --> 00:15:40,503
zoln zikh tsushteln in mark

301
00:15:40,759 --> 00:15:42,474
yidn un polyakn

302
00:15:43,375 --> 00:15:47,959
un zenen ale aroysgeganen oyfn mark, un der vos hot zikh bahaltn

303
00:15:48,387 --> 00:15:52,431
vos m- di daytshn hobn im gekhapt in shtub, hot men im bald dershosn.

304
00:15:52,656 --> 00:15:54,188
un s'iz a por yidn

305
00:15:54,188 --> 00:15:57,104
zenen gevorn dershosn, n- eyner a yunger man

306
00:15:57,145 --> 00:15:59,875
fun nayntsn yor, hot geheysn HILLER

307
00:15:59,875 --> 00:16:02,825
hot men, zey hobn im gefunen oyf UNK boydem ⟨hot er⟩ zikh bahaltn

308
00:16:02,825 --> 00:16:04,515
hot men im dort dershosn.

309
00:16:05,245 --> 00:16:07,854
mir zenen ⟨nor⟩ geshtanen a gantse

310
00:16:08,215 --> 00:16:09,013
tog

311
00:16:09,013 --> 00:16:10,152
in mark

312
00:16:10,152 --> 00:16:11,482
un zey hobn gemakht

313
00:16:11,657 --> 00:16:14,739
bilder farshidene, di GESTAPO

314
00:16:14,982 --> 00:16:19,093
un far nakht hot men undz arayngetribn in a groysn hoyf

315
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:20,798
oyf Varshever gas

316
00:16:21,445 --> 00:16:24,257
un m'hot ongeshtelt mashin gever

317
00:16:25,495 --> 00:16:29,319
un nakher iz ongekumen an ofitsir fun di GESTAPO

318
00:16:29,562 --> 00:16:31,001
un er hot gezogt

319
00:16:31,001 --> 00:16:32,064
"beker

320
00:16:32,064 --> 00:16:33,431
beker mayster

321
00:16:33,431 --> 00:16:34,516
HERAUS"

322
00:16:35,164 --> 00:16:38,724
az di bekers zoln aroysgeyn. hobn zikh di bekers

323
00:16:38,724 --> 00:16:42,994
ver s'iz ganen dortn, ⟨ikh hob zikh⟩ oykh oyfgeshtelt. ikh bin geven, mayne brider

324
00:16:43,332 --> 00:16:46,872
iz geven fir bekers, faktish bekers

325
00:16:46,872 --> 00:16:48,995
nor zenen ganen ongetun tsivil

326
00:16:49,812 --> 00:16:52,624
nisht keyn, mir zenen ongetun vayse fartekher

327
00:16:52,680 --> 00:16:56,673
un zey zenen ongetun tsivil, hot men di fir aroysgenumen.

328
00:16:56,967 --> 00:16:58,884
tsvishn zey iz gevezn

329
00:16:59,008 --> 00:17:01,719
⟨eynem⟩, hot geheysn Moyshe MINSTER

330
00:17:02,147 --> 00:17:04,537
un eyner hot geheysn Shmukler

331
00:17:04,864 --> 00:17:07,966
un eyner hot ge- m'hot im gerufn KAPOCIARZ

332
00:17:07,966 --> 00:17:12,412
un eyner a beker a polyak, un m'hot zey tsugefirt, nisht vayt iz geven di turme

333
00:17:12,412 --> 00:17:14,105
un m'hot zey ale fir dershosn.

334
00:17:15,816 --> 00:17:18,361
der Moyshe MINSTER hot ibergelozt, gehat

335
00:17:18,361 --> 00:17:21,243
yetst geheyrat a froy mit a kleyn kind.

336
00:17:21,688 --> 00:17:25,327
hot ir gedarft in di, in di tsaytn trogn gele lates?

337
00:17:25,992 --> 00:17:28,331
in mayn tsayt iz nokh dos nisht geven

338
00:17:28,877 --> 00:17:30,356
eyder ikh bin avek.

339
00:17:30,463 --> 00:17:35,202
vos iz gevorn mit, mit der mamen un mit di andere shvester brider?

340
00:17:35,202 --> 00:17:37,100
ir hot nokh gevoynt in hoyz

341
00:17:37,100 --> 00:17:38,608
eyder iz zent aroys?

342
00:17:38,310 --> 00:17:40,906
demolst b- ye, ye, bin ikh geven in hoyz.

343
00:17:40,906 --> 00:17:44,632
ikh hob gevoynt bazunder in a tsimer vu ikh hob gefirt mayn varshtat.

344
00:17:44,233 --> 00:17:47,467
ober zey hobn nokh alts gevoynt in hoyz?

345
00:17:46,039 --> 00:17:48,474
zenen ge- UNK ven ikh bin avek

346
00:17:48,474 --> 00:17:52,631
nor mayne tsvey brider, ven mir zenen geven in Rusland

347
00:17:52,637 --> 00:17:54,841
shoyn in Visoke Litovsk

348
00:17:54,966 --> 00:17:56,647
dos iz a shtot

349
00:17:56,890 --> 00:17:59,263
fun ZAPADNA Vaysrusland

350
00:17:59,843 --> 00:18:04,781
di, dos hot a mol balangt tsu Poyln, nor ven di sovyetn zenen arayn

351
00:18:04,787 --> 00:18:06,435
hobn zey dos farnumen

352
00:18:06,812 --> 00:18:12,555
un ikh mit mayne brider zenen geven in di shtot Visoke Litovsk bar a fraynt in, undzers

353
00:18:12,555 --> 00:18:18,284
vos er iz geven a lerer bay undz in shule shpeter vos er hot geshtamt fun di shtot, zenen mir dort ahin

354
00:18:18,284 --> 00:18:20,559
un er hot far undz geshaft arbet dort.

355
00:18:21,004 --> 00:18:23,765
shpeter hobn mir gekrign a briv fun der heym

356
00:18:24,193 --> 00:18:27,224
az s- dos iz geven in shoyn

357
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:30,364
⟨bald⟩ in detsember

358
00:18:30,673 --> 00:18:37,012
az me ken lebn, un mayne briders zenen geven di bekers, vos zey hobn gedorfn arbetn

359
00:18:37,221 --> 00:18:41,602
iz ⟨in di⟩ mayner, iz eyn bruder mayner UNK di brider aheymgeganen

360
00:18:42,165 --> 00:18:44,926
Hershl un Itshe zenen aheymgeganen.

361
00:18:44,629 --> 00:18:45,973
ven iz dos geven?

362
00:18:45,844 --> 00:18:51,018
in, dos iz geven k- in detsember in ferts- in nayn un drayikstn yor.

363
00:18:51,042 --> 00:18:54,124
zenen zey aheymgeganen. mir zenen geven oyf di andere zayt

364
00:18:54,366 --> 00:18:55,806
un zenen umgekumen.

365
00:18:55,806 --> 00:18:57,246
ikh hob nisht gevolt geyn.

366
00:18:58,146 --> 00:19:02,471
az ven ir zayt antlofn, ir zent antlofn mit zey, mit di tsvey

367
00:19:01,268 --> 00:19:02,173
yo

368
00:19:02,471 --> 00:19:07,404
un mit, mit der f- mit di froy, v- zi iz nokh nisht geven farheyrat

369
00:19:04,238 --> 00:19:05,514
mit mayn froy

370
00:19:06,313 --> 00:19:07,758
yo, yo

371
00:19:07,461 --> 00:19:09,362
un az ir fir

372
00:19:09,216 --> 00:19:09,952
yo

373
00:19:10,161 --> 00:19:12,197
un far vos zent ir nisht

374
00:19:11,494 --> 00:19:15,234
zenen avek nokh fun UNK a por mentshn fun UNK shtot

375
00:19:15,325 --> 00:19:18,019
vos iz nakher tsurikgeganen zenen umgekumen.

376
00:19:19,138 --> 00:19:21,106
far vos zaynen di andere

377
00:19:21,417 --> 00:19:23,726
shvester brider oder di mame

378
00:19:23,726 --> 00:19:25,073
nisht antlofn?

379
00:19:25,855 --> 00:19:31,502
s'iz a gro- s'iz a frage vos leyder me ken entfern BUT s'iz shver gevezn

380
00:19:31,930 --> 00:19:36,516
ibertsulozn a muter, un ⟨di tsveyte zakh⟩ hot men nisht gevust dortn

381
00:19:36,516 --> 00:19:46,419
m'hot dortn nisht gelekt keyn honik ven m'iz ariber keyn, oyf di sovetishe zayt. dos iz geven a shver lebn. d- m'hot nisht keyn hoyz, nisht keyn shtub, nisht keyn go- hoy- nisht gornisht

382
00:19:46,425 --> 00:19:48,511
un do hot men, zenen mir geven ayngeordnt

383
00:19:48,653 --> 00:19:54,418
m'hot den gevust az m'vet nemen, m'vet makhn gaz oyvns un m'vet farbrenen mentshn? ver hot zikh dos forgeshtelt?

384
00:19:54,897 --> 00:20:00,066
m'hot gemeynt az ver barn daytsh, ver s'vet blay- ver a mol ver umkumen, ober vos UNK ⟨bay emetsn⟩

385
00:20:00,066 --> 00:20:03,008
azoy vi in ale a- di frierdike, di ershte velt milkhome.

386
00:20:03,148 --> 00:20:08,019
m'vet, ver hot zikh forgeshtelt azolekhene zakhn az m'vet farbrenen mentshn, m'vet farbrenen kinder?

387
00:20:08,498 --> 00:20:10,331
s'iz poshet nisht geven

388
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:16,878
tsun, oyfn gedank, vi hot gekent a mentsh, a daytsh vos er aleyn hot gegat kinder

389
00:20:17,138 --> 00:20:20,743
nemen un hargenen kinder? s'iz dokh nisht tsu banemen.

390
00:20:23,095 --> 00:20:25,822
az ven ir zent antlofn dos ershte mol

391
00:20:25,913 --> 00:20:28,657
in, in ah oktober

392
00:20:29,119 --> 00:20:31,644
in nayn un draysik, vos hot ir mitgenumen?

393
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:33,669
vos ⟨ikh hob⟩ mitgenumen? a PLECAK.

394
00:20:34,823 --> 00:20:36,319
vos iz dortn geven?

395
00:20:36,156 --> 00:20:37,837
a p- a p- a hemd

396
00:20:37,978 --> 00:20:39,553
ir veyst, a por hemder

397
00:20:39,553 --> 00:20:42,383
un, un vos hot, UNK vos hot men gekent

398
00:20:42,383 --> 00:20:45,953
un yo, UNK dermonen ven ⟨m'iz⟩ avek

399
00:20:46,028 --> 00:20:48,100
durkh Malkin, durkh di grenets

400
00:20:48,100 --> 00:20:50,865
iz geshtanen ts- a tsvey TRUCKS

401
00:20:51,158 --> 00:20:57,142
un ineveynik zenen geshtanen tsvey daytshn yedn TRUCK mit, s'iz geshtanen a, a groyser koysh

402
00:20:57,165 --> 00:20:59,617
un m'hot yedn bazukht, vos m'hot gegat.

403
00:20:59,617 --> 00:21:04,618
ikh hob gehat a zeygerl, a fingerl, ⟨bloyz⟩, alts vos m'hot, m'hot gefunen arayngevorfn

404
00:21:05,063 --> 00:21:09,126
b- bazukht yedn eynem. vos far a shtikl tsirung er hot gegat, gelt, vos zol z-

405
00:21:09,126 --> 00:21:14,166
alts tsugenumen arayngevorfn in dem koysh, un nakher nokh tsugegebn a kop un aroysgeshmisn

406
00:21:14,166 --> 00:21:15,696
un mir zenen aribergeganen.

407
00:21:16,015 --> 00:21:17,629
zey hobn dokh gelozt.

408
00:21:17,466 --> 00:21:18,388
bite?

409
00:21:18,040 --> 00:21:19,468
zey hobn gelozt.

410
00:21:18,917 --> 00:21:21,512
iz d- yene tsayt hobn zey gelozt yo geyn

